<p>
  <span class="nym">Evangelist</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>evangelista</i>, from <span class="lang">Ancient Greek</span> <i>εὐαγγελιστής</i> 'bringer of good news'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>A byname for the four Biblical gospel authors. Wycliffite Bible (1395): <i>euangelist</i>.</p>
</div>
  
  
  


